_:N87519f4fd0814970b770a56e7bec4942 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Lord Lemos CMG CBE was appointed as Lord in Waiting (Government Whip) on 22 July 2025.</p>\n\n<p>Lord Lemos joined HMPPS as Lead Non-Executive Board Member on 1 May 2018 and chaired the Agency Board leaving role on 20 March 2025.</p>\n\n<p>He is Chair of Hofesh Shechter Dance Company. He is the author of many publications about social policy and supporting vulnerable people, including The Good Prison: Conscience, crime and punishment published in 2014.</p>\n\n<p>His former roles include Chair of English Heritage, Chair of London Institute of Banking and Finance, Vice-President of the British Board of Film Classification, Chair of Payments UK, the Lending Standards Board, Banking Code Standards Board, Notting Hill Housing, and the Money Advice Service; Deputy Chair and Acting Chair of the British Council; a trustee of London University and Dartington Hall Trust, an Audit Commissioner, a Civil Service Commissioner and a non-executive director of the Crown Prosecution Service.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
